    <!-- Privacy Dialog (shown on first launch) -->
    <string name="privacy_dialog_title">Welcome to KyuubiMask</string>
    <string name="privacy_dialog_message">• Notification content is never stored or transmitted. It is processed in memory and immediately discarded.\n• There is no internet permission — it is impossible for data to leave your device.\n• Only settings are saved locally (list of masked apps, ON/OFF state, vibration pattern).\n• Notification access permission is used solely to mask content; the content itself is never saved.\n• KyuubiMask is fully open-source (Apache 2.0) — anyone can verify the code.\n• Protect your privacy with peace of mind 🦊</string>
    <string name="privacy_dialog_button_ok">Got it</string>

